1. The code for sending message

```java
        X.XMessage rawMessage = (X.XMessage) allArguments[0];
        X.XHeader header = rawMessage.getHeader();
        ContextCarrier contextCarrier  = new ContextCarrier();
        RequestURI request = RequestURI.create(header.getUri());
        AbstractSpan span = ContextManager.createExitSpan(header.getTag(), contextCarrier, request.getGroupId());
        Tags.URL.set(span,header.getUri());
        X.XHeader.Builder newHeader = header.toBuilder();
        newHeader.setTrackId(contextCarrier.getDistributedTraceId().encode());
        span.setOperationName("sent out Message【"+newHeader.getTrackId()+"】");
        span.setComponent(ComponentsDefine.UNDERTOW);
        new StringTag(Constans.CARRIER_LEGION_TRACK_ID_KEY).set(span,newHeader.getTrackId());
        CarrierItem next = contextCarrier.items();
        while (next.hasNext()) {
            next = next.next();
            System.out.println("message=["+header.getTrackId()+"]  traceId=["+contextCarrier.getDistributedTraceId().encode()+"]  sent contextCarrier key="+next.getHeadKey()+",value="+next.getHeadValue());
            newHeader.putContextCarrier(next.getHeadKey(), next.getHeadValue());
        }
        rawMessage = rawMessage.toBuilder().setHeader(newHeader).build();
        allArguments[0] = rawMessage;
```

